name: Oyokal farming community
content:
The Oyokal farming community was a Chiss farming community located on Oyokal within the Chiss Ascendancy. Senior Captain Xodlak'in'daro of the Chiss Expansionary Defense Fleet was born into an obscure family of low prestige in the community. After joining the Fleet, she became a merit adoptive of the Xodlak family.
The Oyokal farming community was mentioned in Timothy Zahn's 2021 novel Thrawn Ascendancy: Greater Good, the second installment of Star Wars: The Ascendancy Trilogy.
